<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/11.11.1/styles/atom-one-dark.min.css">
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/11.11.1/highlight.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-glass-dark">

<div class="pf_main">
    {% include "side.njk" %}
    {% include "header.njk" %}
    <main>
        <section>
            <div class="pf_inner scrollbar_custom pb_100">

                <!-- TIT -->
                <div class="sec_tit">
                    <h2 class="fs_36">Components – Modal</h2>
                    <p class="fs_16 mt_10 txtClr1 lih150per">
                        버튼 클릭으로 특정 모달을 열고, 닫기 버튼·dim·ESC로 닫는 모달 컴포넌트입니다.<br>
                        YouTube 재생, 모달 체인, 오버레이 클릭 옵션 등을 지원하여 다양한 인터랙션을 구현할 수 있습니다.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="pf_container">

                    <!-- ======================================= -->
                    <!-- ATTRIBUTE REFERENCE -->
                    <!-- ======================================= -->
                    <div class="tit">
                        <h3 class="fs_24 fw_medium fc_white1">ATTRIBUTE REFERENCE</h3>
                    </div>

                    <table class="pf_table attr_table mt_20">
                        <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>속성명</th>
                            <th>필수</th>
                            <th>타입 / 예시</th>
                            <th>기본값</th>
                            <th>설명</th>
                        </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>

                        <tr>
                            <td><code>data-modal</code></td>
                            <td>필수</td>
                            <td>string<br><small>"modal_basic"</small></td>
                            <td>-</td>
                            <td>열릴 모달의 <code>id</code> 값을 지정합니다.</td>
                        </tr>

                        <tr>
                            <td><code>data-youtube</code></td>
                            <td>선택</td>
                            <td>string<br><small>"Xx123AbCd"</small></td>
                            <td>-</td>
                            <td>YouTube 영상 ID. iframe에 자동으로 embed URL이 입력됩니다.</td>
                        </tr>

                        <tr>
                            <td><code>data-chain</code></td>
                            <td>선택</td>
                            <td>boolean<br><small>속성 선언만 해도 true</small></td>
                            <td>false</td>
                            <td>활성화 시, 새 모달이 열릴 때 기존 활성 모달을 모두 닫습니다.</td>
                        </tr>

                        <tr>
                            <td><code>.close_modal</code></td>
                            <td>선택</td>
                            <td>class</td>
                            <td>-</td>
                            <td>모달 닫기 버튼 역할을 합니다.</td>
                        </tr>

                        <tr>
                            <td><code>.dim</code></td>
                            <td>필수</td>
                            <td>element</td>
                            <td>-</td>
                            <td>모달 배경 오버레이. 옵션에 따라 클릭 시 모달을 닫습니다.</td>
                        </tr>

                        </tbody>
                    </table>

                    <!-- ======================================= -->
                    <!-- EXAMPLE 1 : BASIC MODAL -->
                    <!-- ======================================= -->
                    <div class="tit mt_100">
                        <h3 class="fs_24 fw_medium fc_white1">EXAMPLE – 기본 모달</h3>
                    </div>

                    <div class="code_wrap pf_box mt_20">
                        <div class="example_wrap dp_f gap20">

                            <button type="button"
                                    class="wv_modal_btn pf_btn1"
                                    data-modal="modal_basic">
                                Open Modal
                            </button>

                            <!-- MODAL -->
                            <div id="modal_basic"
                                 class="wv_modal pf_modal_box"
                                 tabindex="-1">
                                <div class="modal_inner">
                                    <h4 class="fs_20 fw_medium mb_10">Basic Modal</h4>
                                    <p class="mb_20 txtClr1">일반적인 모달 창입니다.</p>
                                    <button type="button"
                                            class="wv_modal_btn close_modal pf_btn1">
                                        닫기
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="dim"></div>

                        </div>

                        <!-- HTML PREVIEW -->
                        <div class="cont_wrap">
                            <div class="dp_f jtf_bet al_center">
                                <p>HTML</p>
                                <button type="button"
                                        class="wv_copy_btn copy_btn"
                                        data-target="hl1"></button>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <pre class="hljs"><code class="language-html pt_0 pb_0 pr_0 pl_0" id="hl1">
    &lt;button type="button" class="wv_modal_btn" data-modal="modal_basic"&gt;
      Open Modal
    &lt;/button&gt;

    &lt;div id="modal_basic" class="wv_modal" tabindex="-1"&gt;
      &lt;div class="modal_inner"&gt;
        &lt;h4&gt;Basic Modal&lt;/h4&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;일반적인 모달 창입니다.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;button type="button" class="wv_modal_btn close_modal"&gt;닫기&lt;/button&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
</code></pre>

                    </div>

                    <p class="fs_16 fw_regular mt_10 txtClr1">
                        <code>data-modal</code> 속성을 사용하여 모달을 열 수 있습니다.
                        닫기는 <code>.close_modal</code> 또는 dim/ESC로 가능합니다.
                    </p>

                    <!-- ======================================= -->
                    <!-- EXAMPLE 2 : YOUTUBE MODAL -->
                    <!-- ======================================= -->
                    <div class="tit mt_100">
                        <h3 class="fs_24 fw_medium fc_white1">EXAMPLE – YouTube 모달</h3>
                    </div>

                    <div class="code_wrap pf_box mt_20">
                        <div class="example_wrap dp_f gap20">

                            <button type="button"
                                    class="wv_modal_btn pf_btn1"
                                    data-modal="modal_youtube"
                                    data-youtube="ScMzIvxBSi4">
                                Open YouTube Modal
                            </button>

                            <!-- YOUTUBE MODAL -->
                            <div id="modal_youtube"
                                 class="wv_modal pf_modal_box"
                                 tabindex="-1">
                                <div class="modal_inner video_wrap">
                                    <iframe src="" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>

                                    <button type="button"
                                            class="wv_modal_btn close_modal pf_btn1 mt_20">
                                        닫기
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>

                        <!-- HTML PREVIEW -->
                        <div class="cont_wrap">
                            <div class="dp_f jtf_bet al_center">
                                <p>HTML</p>
                                <button type="button"
                                        class="wv_copy_btn copy_btn"
                                        data-target="hl2"></button>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <pre class="hljs"><code class="language-html pt_0 pb_0 pr_0 pl_0" id="hl2">
    &lt;button class="wv_modal_btn"
            data-modal="modal_youtube"
            data-youtube="ScMzIvxBSi4"&gt;
      Open YouTube Modal
    &lt;/button&gt;

    &lt;div id="modal_youtube" class="wv_modal" tabindex="-1"&gt;
      &lt;div class="modal_inner"&gt;
        &lt;iframe src="" allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
        &lt;button class="wv_modal_btn close_modal"&gt;닫기&lt;/button&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
</code></pre>

                    </div>

                    <p class="fs_16 fw_regular mt_10 txtClr1">
                        <code>data-youtube</code>를 사용하면 YouTube 영상 ID를 자동으로 iframe에 로드합니다.<br>
                        모달 닫기 시 자동으로 <code>src=""</code>로 초기화되어 영상 재생이 중지됩니다.
                    </p>

                    <!-- ======================================= -->
                    <!-- EXAMPLE 3 : CHAIN MODAL -->
                    <!-- ======================================= -->
                    <div class="tit mt_100">
                        <h3 class="fs_24 fw_medium fc_white1">EXAMPLE – Chain Modal</h3>
                    </div>

                    <div class="code_wrap pf_box mt_20">

                        <div class="example_wrap dp_f gap20">

                            <button type="button"
                                    class="wv_modal_btn pf_btn1"
                                    data-modal="modal_chain_1">
                                Open Modal #1
                            </button>

                            <button type="button"
                                    class="wv_modal_btn pf_btn1"
                                    data-modal="modal_chain_2">
                                Open Modal #2 (Chain)
                            </button>

                            <!-- MODAL 1 -->
                            <div id="modal_chain_1"
                                 class="wv_modal pf_modal_box"
                                 tabindex="-1">
                                <div class="modal_inner">
                                    <h4 class="fs_20">Chain Modal #1</h4>
                                    <button type="button" class="wv_modal_btn pf_btn1"  data-modal="modal_chain_2">#2 열기</button>
                                    <button type="button" class="wv_modal_btn close_modal pf_btn1 mt_20">닫기</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- MODAL 2 (CHAIN) -->
                            <div id="modal_chain_2"
                                 class="wv_modal pf_modal_box"
                                 data-chain
                                 tabindex="-1">
                                <div class="modal_inner">
                                    <h4 class="fs_20">Chain Modal #2</h4>
                                    <p class="txtClr1 mt_10">이 모달이 열리면 다른 활성 모달은 자동으로 닫힙니다.</p>
                                    <button type="button" class="wv_modal_btn close_modal pf_btn1 mt_20">닫기</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>

                        <!-- HTML PREVIEW -->
                        <div class="cont_wrap">
                            <div class="dp_f jtf_bet al_center">
                                <p>HTML</p>
                                <button type="button"
                                        class="wv_copy_btn copy_btn"
                                        data-target="hl3"></button>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <pre class="hljs"><code class="language-html pt_0 pb_0 pr_0 pl_0" id="hl3">
    &lt;button class="wv_modal_btn" data-modal="modal_chain_1"&gt;Open Modal #1&lt;/button&gt;
    &lt;button class="wv_modal_btn" data-modal="modal_chain_2"&gt;Open Modal #2&lt;/button&gt;

    &lt;div id="modal_chain_1" class="wv_modal"&gt; ... &lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;div id="modal_chain_2" class="wv_modal" data-chain&gt;
      ...
    &lt;/div&gt;
</code></pre>

                    </div>

                    <p class="fs_16 fw_regular mt_10 txtClr1">
                        <code>data-chain</code>이 선언된 모달은 열릴 때 기존 활성 모달을 모두 닫고 단독으로 표시됩니다.
                    </p>

                </div>

            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</div>

